[alarm sounding]

33:26.547 --> 33:27.912
Final warning.

33:28.007 --> 33:30.464
Manual override failed.

33:30.551 --> 33:34.965
- Step away from the computer.
- I'm so sorry. I can't do that.

33:35.055 --> 33:38.889
Manual override failed.
Counter-measures will begin.

33:38.976 --> 33:40.807
Hey!

33:42.563 --> 33:44.895
One minute to contamination.

33:46.275 --> 33:48.982
Wanna release the gas?
You'll die with the rest of us.

33:49.069 --> 33:53.312
No, no. I'm not trying to release it.
I'm trying to render it inert.

33:53.407 --> 33:56.899
Juliet, ljust want to make it safe.

33:59.205 --> 34:00.365
[grunting]

34:00.456 --> 34:02.697
Forty seconds to contamination.

34:13.928 --> 34:16.544
Thirty seconds to contamination.

34:22.436 --> 34:25.178
Warning: contamination imminent.

34:25.272 --> 34:26.887
Evacuate immediate/y.

34:26.982 --> 34:30.725
- [grunting]
- [Faraday] Hey!

34:41.455 --> 34:43.616
Twenty seconds to contamination.

34:43.707 --> 34:46.198
Whatever he's doing, tell him to stop.

34:46.293 --> 34:49.626
We're trying to disable it
before he can use it against us.

34:50.422 --> 34:52.003
Juliet...

34:53.050 --> 34:55.666
...look me in the eye
and tell me you are certain

34:55.761 --> 34:59.595
Benjamin Linus wouldn't use this gas
to kill everyone on this island!

34:59.682 --> 35:01.923
We know he's used it before.

35:02.017 --> 35:04.429
If you wanna stop us,
you have to shoot us both.

35:04.520 --> 35:06.181
Ten seconds to contamination.

35:06.272 --> 35:08.103
- Daniel!
- Yeah, I'm trying.

35:09.858 --> 35:12.019
Come on!

35:12.111 --> 35:13.100
Come on!

35:13.195 --> 35:14.230
