35:15.155 --> 35:16.531
...four...

35:17.366 --> 35:19.357
...three...

35:19.451 --> 35:21.282
...two...

35:23.372 --> 35:26.364
[computer tone]

35:29.712 --> 35:32.203
[pressure valves hissing]

35:50.607 --> 35:54.065
That... that was a close one.

36:02.786 --> 36:04.242
[knocking on door]

36:15.632 --> 36:17.964
- What are you reading?
- Shephard's file.

36:18.052 --> 36:19.588
Mikhail dropped it off.

36:22.222 --> 36:24.383
He's a spinal surgeon, Ben.

36:24.475 --> 36:27.433
He has extensive experience
in tumor removal.

36:30.939 --> 36:33.021
- How about that?
- He can help you.

36:39.948 --> 36:43.691
I thought you'd be more excited.
What's wrong?

36:47.539 --> 36:49.530
I need you to come with me.

36:55.798 --> 37:00.462
After our last raid on the tail-section
survivors, they ran off, left the beach.

37:02.054 --> 37:06.297
I sent Pickett and Tom to track
their location. They came across this.

37:07.267 --> 37:09.053
I'm sorry, Juliet.

37:09.144 --> 37:11.135
Sorry about what?

37:13.982 --> 37:15.893
Oh, my God.

37:16.527 --> 37:18.313
Oh, my God.

37:18.404 --> 37:21.111
Oh, my God! Oh, my God!

37:22.783 --> 37:23.989
Oh, my God!

37:27.079 --> 37:29.195
Goodwin.

37:29.289 --> 37:31.280
[sobbing]

37:31.375 --> 37:32.706
What happened?

37:33.836 --> 37:36.748
We don't know.
There weren't any witnesses.

37:36.839 --> 37:40.047
I can only assume they found out
he wasn't one of them.

37:41.969 --> 37:45.837
- Guess I should've listened to you.
- Why are you showing me this?

37:49.852 --> 37:52.264
Why did you bring me out here?

37:52.813 --> 37:55.350
What, you mean instead of his wife?

38:01.572 --> 38:03.779
You knew this would happen.

38:06.952 --> 38:10.410
You sent him out here because
you knew this would happen.

38:11.081 --> 38:14.869
You wanted this.
You wanted him to die!

38:16.962 --> 38:18.077
VVhy?

38:19.089 --> 38:21.171
VVhy?

38:22.759 --> 38:24.966
You're asking me why?

38:25.762 --> 38:30.222
After everything I did to get you here,
everything I've done to keep you here,

38:30.309 --> 38:32.766
how can you possibly not understand...

38:34.771 --> 38:36.762
...that you're mine?

38:44.740 --> 38:46.446
Take as much time as you need.

38:53.499 --> 38:55.490
[sobbing]

39:00.631 --> 39:02.747
[electrical zapping]

39:11.350 --> 39:14.092
Whoa! Kate, it's all right.
They're on our side.

39:14.186 --> 39:17.849
"Our side," Juliet?
She just knocked me unconscious.

39:17.940 --> 39:21.478
Yeah. I'm very sorry about that,
but I had no choice!

39:24.154 --> 39:27.112
Look, Daniel's inside
securing the facility.

39:27.199 --> 39:30.111
If you come with me,
I'll be more than happy to explain

39:30.202 --> 39:32.443
exactly how we just saved your life!

39:36.416 --> 39:38.372
All right, let's go.

39:42.172 --> 39:44.163
I'll take their word for it.

39:52.975 --> 39:54.636
You OK?

39:59.273 --> 40:01.229
He wanted me to kill them.

40:04.319 --> 40:06.605
Ben. He told me to kill both of them.

40:12.160 --> 40:15.402
- How can he tell you anything?
- I don't know.

40:15.497 --> 40:19.786
But he knew how to get to me, knew where
they were going, what they were doing.

40:19.876 --> 40:21.707
Don't you understand?

40:21.795 --> 40:25.083
These people came here
to wage war against Ben.

40:26.174 --> 40:28.085
And Ben's gonna win, Jack.

40:29.595 --> 40:32.678
And when he does, you don't
want to be anywhere near me.

40:34.349 --> 40:35.680
Why not?

40:39.229 --> 40:41.345
Because he thinks that I'm his.

40:44.192 --> 40:46.729
And he knows how I feel about you.

41:10.093 --> 41:12.300
He knows where to find me.

41:31.907 --> 41:33.317
Oh!

41:34.242 --> 41:35.652
Beat that.

41:44.586 --> 41:47.293
- [laughing]
- Son of a bitch!

41:49.132 --> 41:51.418
How'd you get so damn good
at horseshoes?

41:51.551 --> 41:53.758
I don't know. Guess I'm just lucky.

42:01.603 --> 42:03.810
What the hell are you doing out?

42:04.773 --> 42:06.104
See you guys at dinner.
